Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:26.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:28.36,Main,,0,0,0,,"Construction" "We apologize for the inconvenience"\N"We appreciate your understanding"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,"Class A River 'River Styx' (Hades)"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:35.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Could this be... the River Styx?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:39.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Come here... Come to this side...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.96,Main,,0,0,0,,This side is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:45.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything's a blast here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:48.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be scared, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:50.63,Main,,0,0,0,,This side is nice in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji, why are you on that side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:57.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be frightened, Akihisa.\NAs you can see, I'm just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:59.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to\Nworry about anything, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:04.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to this side!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:15.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi!! Question: Alone or together,{\i0}\N{\i1}which one is wonderful?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.96,0:01:34.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My future starts spinning colorfully{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How much should I tell him?{\i0}\N{\i1}Should I pretend I didn't see?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:45.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see, this vast world{\i0}\N{\i1}grows based on my mood{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:51.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you today, I really love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so stupid... My stupidity is greater{\i0}\N{\i1}than the number of the stars in the sky{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:02:02.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't admit my feelings for you,{\i0}\N{\i1}but I had a dream of walking with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry... It's just,{\i0}\N{\i1}I didn't know it was love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:14.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The answer is, you and mystery{\i0}\N{\i1}plus me equals infinite jump!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:36.03,Main,,0,0,0,,"BAKA and TEST\N-Summon the Beasts 2-"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:42.12,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Episode 2\NMe, Yukata, and Festivities!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't remember much, but\NI feel like I went through hell, literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:50.46,Main,,0,0,0,,When your delirious\Nramblings became a conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:52.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought that you\Nwere goners, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:56.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised... that we're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akihisa and Yuuji made{\i0}\N{\i1}a challenge to hit on girls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:04.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The girls found that out and{\i0}\N{\i1}gave them punishment. Teehee.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,At any rate, what a\Nhorrible punishment that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:11.82,Main,,0,0,0,,To think that they did not only that,\Nbut they also used something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.69,Main,,0,0,0,,But this is rather unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:17.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we did something pretty terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:22.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It was extremely rude of you to go\Nhit on other girls when you're with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:25.71,Main,,0,0,0,,But considering what\Nwe did, we got off easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,People don't call having a\Nnear-death experience getting off easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:32.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It's hard to think that they'd\Nlet us off the hook this easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:34.05,Main,,0,0,0,,There may be more to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.67,Main,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Yuuji? Should we run?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.22,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this about "running"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:53.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you guys went and\Nchanged into {\i1}yukata{\i0}, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:56.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, they're holding a festival, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, that looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.41,Main,,0,0,0,,This might be my\Nfirst time wearing {\i1}yukata{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:10.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. You grew up overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:17.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What, Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:21.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You were admiring\NMinami just now, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She's especially cute in a {\i1}yukata{\i0}, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kimonos {\i0}are nice since\Nthey make you look good
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,even if you have small breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I have no idea what\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:38.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez... If you have no idea,\Nthen I'll show you. Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's a peep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,See? His reaction was\Nquicker than usual, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:51.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! Hang in there, Muttsulini!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:57.30,Main,,0,0,0,,This may look bad, but it isn't, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you think of me in a {\i1}yukata{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose you look good in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:11.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Then do you wanna marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:12.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:16.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Then do you wanna get engaged to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Not even a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.40,Main,,0,0,0,,No way, Jose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna keep breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:26.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! You're really cute, Shouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't fight your feelings, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You threatened me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:35.67,Main,,0,0,0,,My mom told me to do whatever it\Ntakes when it comes to relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on with{\i0}\N{\i1}Himeji and the others...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:43.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought they were all upset.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the festival now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:56.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Akira. We don't want to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.78,Main,,0,0,0,,This is only my second time\Ngoing to a festival in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.53,Main,,0,0,0,,so I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:03.49,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:14.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's lively, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:16.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it seems fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Döner kebab?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:20.21,Main,,0,0,0,,They look delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Then let's try some.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:24.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,This is your punishment\Nfor earlier. You go buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't have said that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you like to eat them,\Ntoo, Aki? I'll go buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:43.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have no objection...\NWait... What?! You'll buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.12,Main,,0,0,0,,No, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:53.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why...? It couldn't be{\i0}\N{\i1}that she forgave me, could it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:58.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like to try many other things, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:05.38,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay. You go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:08.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess they don't use lamb in\NJapan, huh? Here, you have some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:24.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Aki, you got sauce on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:29.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:34.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa! I bought some octopus\Ndumplings. Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:38.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mizuki. Then, I'll have one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Say ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:42.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:44.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:49.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, no... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, say ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:53.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:59.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm... The pancake part is hot\Nand creamy and the octopus is chewy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:03.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like that, Sis!\NThis isn't illicit sexual activity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.74,Main,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--It wasn't good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:10.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:13.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What did you screw up this time, Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:17.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Getting worked up over a festival?\NYou're really childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:20.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Me? It's {\i1}you {\i0}who's really getting worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:23.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-They said they'd give\Nthese to me for free, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:27.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You lived in Germany so long,\Nso you couldn't help it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:30.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, would you like\Nsome cotton candy? It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.72,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.89,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:41.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go, say ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:46.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, it tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji... would you like\Nsome {\i1}yakisoba {\i0}noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:54.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I guess I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I got {\i1}okonomiyaki{\i0}, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That's considerate of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's some {\i1}ramune {\i0}soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:04.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good, Yuuji was forgiven, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}--This is a festival after all. They'd want{\i0}\N{\i1}to enjoy it rather than be upset, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:13.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa! I saw some color\Nbaby chickens over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought they went extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:18.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... they just paint the baby chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:22.10,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Then it wasn't\Nbecause of their breed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not possible! Right, Muttsulini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:30.28,Main,,0,0,0,,"Color Baby Chickens"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.28,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Cheep, cheep, cheep..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:31.49,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Cheep, cheep, cheep..."\N"Grab!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.28,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Cheep, cheep, cheep..."\N"Grab!" "Cheeeeep?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:33.03,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Rumble, rumble, rumble..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.28,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Rumble, rumble, rumble..."\N"Sneer"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:37.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll color you however I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:40.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That's common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:43.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki, are you enjoying the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji, are you having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:48.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Y... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Akihisa, there's a fun\Nevent going on here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:57.10,Main,,0,0,0,,"The First Summer 'Miss {\i1}Yukata{\i0}'\NBeauty Contest"... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:58.39,Main,,0,0,0,,A beauty contest, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.89,Main,,0,0,0,,That sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Good photo opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:03.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Or better yet, why not have\Neveryone compete in the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:11.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, I'm not saying\Nyou must or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:15.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought that might be\Na nice summer memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:16.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's participate, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll stay in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's compete in the event...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.09,Main,,0,0,0,,...let's have {\i1}everyone here {\i0}compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:41.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,We're all participating in the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:48.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:51.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, you guys aren't making any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:53.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitting on girls earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:55.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Surely you didn't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:58.70,Main,,0,0,0,,that you were off the hook after\Nthat little punishment you got earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:03.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I have a makeup kit on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:07.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! With my frame, there's no\Nway I could dress up as a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:10.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Please satisfy your anger by\Ndressing Akihisa up as a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:14.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to weasel out of\Nthis by yourself?! You frickin' traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:17.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You both don't know when to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:20.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you follow the example\Nof Tsuchiya who gave up like a man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:25.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Cruel... This is so cruel, Hideyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:30.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's not in my nature to go easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:33.53,Main,,0,0,0,,...since makeup is one of\Nthe techniques for theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:34.65,Main,,0,0,0,,"Akiko Yoshii"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you guys have\Nto put your all into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:38.78,Main,,0,0,0,,"Koumi Tsuchiya"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:42.24,Main,,0,0,0,,How humiliating...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:45.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Koumi Tsuchiya...? What on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,"Hong Xiong Li"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:49.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got it easy, Muttsulini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm dressed up as a woman, and on top\Nof that, I'm supposed to be a foreigner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:58.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true that people could see a\Nfemale foreign athlete having your frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.72,Main,,0,0,0,,All three of you look good with makeup on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you look very cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:08.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki, your sister is happy\Nthat you grew up to be pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:11.69,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not something that\Nyou should say to your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Your sex appeal needs work, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:17.74,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys forced me to\Nwear this! Don't complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:22.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it... why am\NI being forced to compete, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, that's the default for this show.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot Test!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:36.05,Main,,0,0,0,,"The First Summer..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:40.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's start the First Summer\N"Miss {\i1}Yukata{\i0}" Beauty Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:45.01,Main,,0,0,0,,"First Summer 'Miss {\i1}Yukata{\i0}' Beauty Contest"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,As a commentator, we have\NMr. Obata who's also wearing {\i1}yukata{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:50.73,Main,,0,0,0,,He's a sponsor of the event and\Nwill be the judge for the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to\Nseeing pretty women in {\i1}yukata{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.48,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Akiko Yoshii"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:13:00.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! They won't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:05.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji, if you believe\Nin yourself, you can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you nuts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:12.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to record your cute side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Our only option is to lose\Nquickly and get out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! If we tell them we're guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.60,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:28.06,Main,,0,0,0,,There might be school affiliates\Nor acquaintances in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:31.27,Main,,0,0,0,,If someone finds out, not only will\Nthey think we like dressing up as women,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:33.94,Main,,0,0,0,,but they'll also think that we're so\Nconfident we participated in a contest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:35.40,Main,,0,0,0,,and we have a habit of showing off,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.98,Main,,0,0,0,,which means we'll appear\Nincredibly pathetic in their eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:42.28,Main,,0,0,0,,If that happens,\Nmy social credibility will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think you have any\Nsocial credibility to start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:48.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen up! The only strategy\Nfor us to get out of this crisis is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:51.87,Main,,0,0,0,,to get eliminated in the preliminary\Nround without revealing that we're guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:14:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,This is our battle for manhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:04.05,Main,,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much for your support."\N"Part 1. The End."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:08.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, contestant No. 1,\Nplease step out onto the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:15.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now... what should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Please tell us your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:21.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have my face down.{\i0}\N{\i1}I'll answer as softly as I can, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:24.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I'm Akiko Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:28.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Sounds like you're\Na shy person, Miss Akiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:32.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I find that pure nature of\Nhers cute. She gets a high score.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have any special talents?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:39.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I tell a total lie, it's possible{\i0}\N{\i1}they'll find it out if they question me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:41.72,Main,,0,0,0,,If I must say, it'd be cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:44.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I make things like paella\Nand spaghetti carbonara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:46.55,Main,,0,0,0,,So you cook at home, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, more or less every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:52.31,Main,,0,0,0,,It's rare to see a young\Nwoman like you these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:56.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:15:01.94,Main,,0,0,0,,This is good news for guys.\NWhat do you think, Mr. Obata?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:06.20,Main,,0,0,0,,If you give me your cell number,\NI'll give you some spending money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:09.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, if he wasn't our sponsor,\NI would've decked him good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, Miss Akiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,what were you careful about\Nwhen you put on a {\i1}yukata {\i0}today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I tried to avoid showing my body lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:19.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:23.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Obata, do you have any questions\Nabout her manner of wearing a {\i1}yukata{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:27.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know if she's wearing underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Underwear?! Does he mean women's underwear?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:32.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not wearing that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:40.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for answering\Na surprisingly crude question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:46.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice high score!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:48.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Please tell us your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,My name is Koumi Tsuchiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:58.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you come here to swim today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:15:59.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:01.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you often wear {\i1}yukata{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:02.96,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you come with your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Are they here in the audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:09.64,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:11.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:15.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, besides {\i1}yukata{\i0},\Nwhat kind of clothes do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:17.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Silk Chinese dresses, {\i1}kimono{\i0},\Nand outfits for race car girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:20.86,Main,,0,0,0,,cheerleaders, nurses, flight attendants,\Nwaitresses at family restaurants, and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:24.32,Main,,0,0,0,,policewomen. Also leotards, lady's suits,\Nsailor school uniforms, school blazers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,shrine maiden outfits,\Nmaid uniforms and tennis outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:28.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I think they're wonderf-- Err, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.95,Main,,0,0,0,,That was surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:37.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Despite your coolheaded attitude,\NMiss Koumi, you seem to like cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:38.75,Main,,0,0,0,,P-Please forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Koumi! Koumi! Koumi! Koumi! Koumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:48.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What a reaction... She's definitely\Ngoing to make it to the final round.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Really, you can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice own goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.90,Main,,0,0,0,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:07.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Hong Xiong Li. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:12.45,Main,,0,0,0,,She's quite tall, isn't she?\NWhat do you think, Mr. Obata?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:17.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Wonderful! I love tall women.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:18.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:21.67,Main,,0,0,0,,She's got a high mark from the judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:23.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have any other questi-- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,How does Cambodia\Nsound for our honeymoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.97,Main,,0,0,0,,We're from different countries!\NI can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.89,Main,,0,0,0,,With love, all things are possible, my honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:36.89,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm confident that love will emerge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:42.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,We can start off as friends. I'll take\Ngood care of you the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:51.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Enough, already! I'm gonna\Nbeat you up, old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:54.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You can do anything you like to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:58.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I will not permit an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:03.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouko?! Why is this considered an affair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got a scar in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.59,Main,,0,0,0,,This summer has become\Nunforgettable in many ways, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:16.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I can no longer get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:19.52,Main,,0,0,0,,It was good that the contest got suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:22.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It was a disaster to the sponsor, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:24.40,Main,,0,0,0,,We went overboard, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we let them off the hook now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:28.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Extenuating circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:32.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're sorry.\NLet's make an exception and forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:38.62,Main,,0,0,0,,But I wonder who would've\Nwon if the contest went on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:41.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, wouldn't Hideyoshi\Nbe the most appropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:46.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you think the word "appropriate"\Nis wrong, considering that I'm a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:50.01,Main,,0,0,0,,My heart went pitter-patter when\NI saw Muttsulini in women's clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:51.46,Main,,0,0,0,,How about you, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:55.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, since I'm used to\Nseeing Aki in women's clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:58.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I liked the other two. It was refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:19:01.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, Sis! I don't\Nwear women's clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:04.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you saying, Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:09.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You wore a skirt again last night,\Nright...? While you were asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:12.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! What'd you do to\Nme while I was asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:15.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. That's half a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:20.58,Main,,0,0,0,,A lie? How can you make\Nwhat you just said half a lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I only made you wear it up to your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Then you made me wear it half way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:28.04,Main,,0,0,0,,No. The industry\Nterminology would be "halfway-off."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:29.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Halfway-off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:32.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, guys! They're pretty much done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.43,Main,,0,0,0,,This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:39.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Sakamoto really is skilled\Nin these things, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:41.18,Main,,0,0,0,,My proud husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:45.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to cook, too,\Nbut Akihisa didn't let me help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:48.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't hurt myself with\Na kitchen knife or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not the problem, Himeji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:54.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The problem is, you could kill people{\i0}\N{\i1}even without using a kitchen knife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll die if we eat what she makes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:58.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Killer food...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't let her make such dangerous food.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:05.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, how about this time we have\Na cooking competition among us girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll ask the guys to be the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why'd you go and say that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:12.75,Main,,0,0,0,,But how can a cooking winner be decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:18.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think either a knockout{\i0}\N{\i1}or a technical knockout.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:24.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we did eat a lot, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:28.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Somehow I still feel a little hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.77,Main,,0,0,0,,But we have no food left to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:32.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped. I guess we'll get it locally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:33.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Get it locally?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:36.03,Main,,0,0,0,,There's an ocean in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Fresh clams taste good when grilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:45.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I baked madeleines at home and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:52.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yuuji! Let's find clams!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's gather so many that\Nwe won't be able to eat anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:21:00.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Beaches at night are refined\Nand nice too, right, Muttsulini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:02.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I love clams!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:03.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened to them.
